      "title": "Voting in Parliament today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The referendum on the interim relief proposed by President Ranil Wickremesinghe on the 30th will be held in Parliament today.",
        "The debate on interim relief for 2022 will be held for the third day today.",
        "Accordingly, after the discussion is over this evening, a vote on the contribution will be held. (R)"
